1
00:00:01,770 --> 00:00:04,230
Guys! I see an island!

2
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:06,220
Hmm...

3
00:00:06,820 --> 00:00:08,600
Looks like it's an uninhabited island.

4
00:00:08,740 --> 00:00:11,580
Ready the anchor! We'll land on the island!

5
00:00:12,030 --> 00:00:14,540
Well then, go find some foodstuffs.

6
00:00:14,790 --> 00:00:15,860
Yeah!

7
00:00:16,020 --> 00:00:18,410
Listen. No rats or frogs, okay?

8
00:00:18,460 --> 00:00:22,710
How self-centered you are. Once it's in your stomach, it's all the same.

9
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:33,560
Hey, Chopper. Were you able to find any medicinal herbs?

10
00:00:33,740 --> 00:00:38,860
Yep. I've collected most of them, but there may be even rarer ones on this island.

11
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:42,060
More importantly, something's been bugging me for a while.

12
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:46,120
I wonder what this weird groove is that runs down this path...

13
00:00:46,220 --> 00:00:48,220
Come to think of it, yeah, I wonder what it is.

14
00:00:48,540 --> 00:00:50,900
It looks as if a bicycle passed by.

15
00:00:51,220 --> 00:00:53,490
Hey, hey. This is an uninhabited island, right?

16
00:00:53,620 --> 00:00:56,360
This can't be a trace of a bicycle when there's no one here.

17
00:00:57,140 --> 00:00:58,400
That's true.

18
00:00:59,120 --> 00:01:01,870
Hey, we're almost through the jungle!

19
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:07,680
We're suddenly out in a large open space.

20
00:01:08,300 --> 00:01:09,020
Ahh!

21
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:12,300
What's with Chopper?

22
00:01:12,540 --> 00:01:15,300
He's headed to that rock. Is there something there?

23
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,200
Ahh!

24
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,930
That darn Chopper!

25
00:01:19,980 --> 00:01:22,680
He must be trying to have that huge mushroom all to himself!

26
00:01:22,780 --> 00:01:23,720
Hold it!

27
00:01:26,610 --> 00:01:28,060
What's the matter, Chopper?!

28
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:30,530
Looks like something happened. Let's go!

29
00:01:30,780 --> 00:01:32,990
Ow, ow, ow... Hm?

30
00:01:32,850 --> 00:01:36,800
Havy HQ Admiral













Aokiji

31
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:35,070
Whoa! What the heck is this?!

32
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:41,920
Ahh... Hmm?

33
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,250
A raccoon dog?

34
00:01:44,100 --> 00:01:45,870
I'm a reindeer! See? I've got antlers!

35
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:48,130
Are you okay, Chopper?!

36
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,420
Who the heck is this?!

37
00:01:51,460 --> 00:01:52,630
What happened?!

38
00:01:53,130 --> 00:01:54,680
What's going on, Luffy?!

39
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:56,800
What's with you guys?

40
00:01:57,260 --> 00:01:58,510
What's with you?!

41
00:01:59,470 --> 00:02:01,480
Wh-Who's that huge guy?

42
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,480
Who's that guy?!

43
00:02:11,860 --> 00:02:12,860
Robin!

44
00:02:14,660 --> 00:02:15,990
What's wrong, Robin-chan?!

45
00:02:16,380 --> 00:02:17,220
Robin!

46
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:20,410
Wh... Why are you frozen?

47
00:02:20,990 --> 00:02:21,920
Robin...

48
00:02:22,620 --> 00:02:24,040
Oh-ho-ho?

49
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:27,620
Now, now. Don't be so bloodthirsty, guys.

50
00:02:28,130 --> 00:02:30,540
It's not like I'm here on orders.

51
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:33,380
Since it's a nice day, I took a stroll here.

52
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:36,170
Orders?! From what organization?!

53
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:45,220
Oh, my, my, you've turned into a good-looking woman...

54
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:46,940
Nico Robin.

55
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:55,390
It's all right! Now let's move forward

56
00:02:55,650 --> 00:02:58,860
with the sun always in our hearts

57
00:02:59,020 --> 00:03:02,320
As power passes through our clasped hands

58
00:03:02,460 --> 00:03:06,000
Let's grab hold of our wishes

59
00:03:13,570 --> 00:03:19,110
Translation
 FUNimation

60
00:03:13,570 --> 00:03:19,810
Working together, let's ride the giant waves

61
